data.description: Bay Area living can be yours! This beautiful home has so much to offer and features 3 bedrooms and 2 baths, granite countertops and stainless steel appliances for the chef of the home and low maintenance yard (great for entertaining). There is a full bedroom and bathroom on main level that makes the perfect office or is suitable for the multigenerational family or for welcoming overnight guests. Walk upstairs and you are welcomed by a spacious loft/alcove area to make into a separate living space or creative project. The second floor also provides two more bedrooms and full bath. This home One car garage, used for guest area but garage still in tact. This home has incredible potential  to make it your own. Come take a look today!
